  <md:title>50 years Journey of IC Technology_Appendix I</md:title>
  <md:abstract>This describes the history of development in the fields of Sold State Technology, Electronics,IC Technology, Computer, Super-Computer, microprocessor chips , local area network(LAN) and submarine cables.</md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>ab6c5ed6-521a-43b3-bf3f-7c8643a64626</md:uuid>
